divs: Sighting DetailsI WAS AT MY APARTMENT LOOKING THROUGH MY CELESTRON ADVANCED GT 9" TELESCOPE. AND POINTING IT AT THE MOON WHEN I SAW A OBJECT WITH BLINKING LIGHTS HOVERING ABOVE THE MOON WHEN I SAW IT I LOOKED CLOSER AND I SAW PIPES FROM THE SHIP TO THE MOON. WHEN I TRIED TO TAKE A PHOTO WITH MY DIGITAL CAMERA I DIDENT SEE IT BUT WHEN I LOOKED THROUGH THE EYEPIECE I SAW IT SO IT WAS INVISIBLE TO MY DIGITAL CAMERA I ALSO THE DAY BEFORE SAW ANOTHER SHIP WITH THE SAME CHARECTERISTICS FLOATING THROUGH THE SKY
